{"tid":1567561,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超球證主席認VAR首月4宗誤判","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:39:46.000Z","uid":17506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f568cbddfda70e51242b664dfd68a62704d15a12","tid":1567561,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】視像裁判（VAR）今季首度應用於英超，1個月來卻爭議不斷。球證主席萊利昨承認四度誤判，包括上月底曼城中場大衛施華被踩腳，球證未有判罰12碼。<br />\n<br />\n英超球證主席萊利昨證實，英超開季1個月以來，錄得4宗誤判。球證在上月曼城作客般尼茅夫一役，大衛施華遭主隊中場謝法臣拿馬踩腳，但未獲12碼。般尼茅夫在一周後作客李斯特城，則有卡林威爾遜被泰利文斯侵犯，後者避過紅牌。而紐卡素上月底迎戰屈福特，中場艾錫希頓扳平前犯手球在先，VAR未有示意，令客軍無辜失分。韋斯咸同日迎戰諾域治，施巴斯坦賀拿被撞跌後，則未獲12碼。<br />\n<br />\n萊利透露，部分漏判是球證不希望影響賽事流暢度，又表示VAR表現不完美，但可接受，承諾今周開始會改善，讓VAR團隊更決斷地介入賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20190914/s00015/1568399650083/%e8%8b%b1%e8%b6%85%e7%90%83%e8%ad%89%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%ad%e8%aa%8dvar%e9%a6%96%e6%9c%884%e5%ae%97%e8%aa%a4%e5%88%a4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20190914%2Fs00015%2F1568399650083%2F%25e8%258b%25b1%25e8%25b6%2585%25e7%2590%2583%25e8%25ad%2589%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%25b8%25ad%25e8%25aa%258dvar%25e9%25a6%2596%25e6%259c%25884%25e5%25ae%2597%25e8%25aa%25a4%25e5%2588%25a4&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=b6e25508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20190914%2Fs00015%2F1568399650083%2F%25e8%258b%25b1%25e8%25b6%2585%25e7%2590%2583%25e8%25ad%2589%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%25b8%25ad%25e8%25aa%258dvar%25e9%25a6%2596%25e6%259c%25884%25e5%25ae%2597%25e8%25aa%25a4%25e5%2588%25a4&h=eb773740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20190914/s00015/1568399650083/%e8%8b%b1%e8%b6%85%e7%90%83%e8%ad%89%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%ad%e8%aa%8dvar%e9%a6%96%e6%9c%884%e5%ae%97%e8%aa%a4%e5%88%a4</a>"},{"pid":"02427ec1cad917675e423ea91240d8958c7a2063","tid":1567561,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb2d865efb7ae5459d4bf7de50c56d16c76fcf8","tid":1567561,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da175d2c348196ae05dee0d60acb1bb179729a1e","tid":1567561,"uid":53672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"又表示VAR表現不完美，但可接受，承諾今周開始會改善，讓VAR團隊更決斷地介入賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a34ff669fd186b36a91641b1d81b2b9e2832483","tid":1567561,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da175d2c348196ae05dee0d60acb1bb179729a1e","tid":1567561,"uid":53672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"又表示VAR表現不完美，但可接受，承諾今周開始會改善，讓VAR團隊更決斷地介入賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"警犬"},{"pid":"8ad5c67fd21c311580091ea3e5b567102bc3c557","tid":1567561,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:28:18.000Z","msg":"點解唔比埋主球證睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22504a254d2ffef3cea6e935a9ceacc4007e1f36","tid":1567561,"uid":17506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:30:00.000Z","msg":"2019年8月25日 般尼茅夫 1 - 3 曼城<br />\n2019年8月31日 李斯特城 3 - 1 般尼茅夫<br />\n2019年8月31日 紐卡素 1 - 1 屈福特<br />\n2019年8月31日 韋斯咸 2 - 0 諾域治<br />\n<br />\n應該係呢4場"},{"pid":"5521d6a483b5c5275ddc1ca10899386d85a588ec","tid":1567561,"uid":17506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ad5c67fd21c311580091ea3e5b567102bc3c557","tid":1567561,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:28:18.000Z","msg":"點解唔比埋主球證睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"部分漏判是球證不希望影響賽事流暢度，又表示VAR表現不完美，但可接受，承諾今周開始會改善，讓VAR團隊更決斷地介入賽事<br />\n<br />\n同香港政府個態度一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190818cb3605058c77be3159547edeed687e4e8c","tid":1567561,"uid":69754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"成日走甩12碼"},{"pid":"89f416ace482c1c68b3cde8d2229b5ca9bbb0bdc","tid":1567561,"uid":69568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"Riley呢d賤種狗都做到主席 就知呢個會同香港政府冇分別"},{"pid":"32d26fd5382c24f8aa9d81748d88c96087d7ab21","tid":1567561,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"英超今季首次應用到VAR協助裁判執法，使用數周已經引來不少爭議和討論，英超裁判協會亦有開會檢討VAR成效和運作，協會主席Mike Riley承認，經過覆核後，確認在頭四周賽事中，<span style=\"color: red;\">VAR系統在四宗誤判個案中，未有即時向場上的球證作出正確指示，當中包括兩球12碼、一球誤判入球，以及一張漏判的紅牌。</span><br />\n英超裁判協會表示，這四宗誤判個案分別出現在第三周和第四周的3場賽事，第三周曼城作客般尼茅夫，上半場大衛施華在禁區被謝法臣拿馬踩中，球證和VAR當時並未示意12碼，最後覆核為誤判個案。至於第四周，韋斯咸的施巴斯坦賀拿被諾域治的泰布爾侵犯，同樣是12碼漏判個案。另外李斯特城的泰利文斯踩中般尼茅夫的哥林威爾遜，應被紅牌驅逐離場，以法比安舒亞為紐卡素追平屈福特的一球，都出現誤判的情況，但VAR系統未有即時指正球證作出正確的判決。<br />\n協會主席Mike Riley承認VAR球證的犯錯，表示會從錯誤中學習力求進步：「我們試圖不破壞比賽的進程，但在這四個情況下，VAR應該意識到這是明顯的誤判，因此我們會不斷學習，希望改善運作。而事實上VAR在頭四周有正面的表現，例如我們推翻了6次場上的吹罰，指示球證作出正確的判決，都是正面的效果。」<br />\nRiley又指出，VAR系統今季檢視了227宗事件，推翻了6次場上的裁決，但同時亦有10次裁決是理應被推翻的。VAR系統在2018年首次在英國賽事使用，2017-18賽季在足總盃個別賽事試行，上季亦有在英超賽事試用，但僅用作場邊監察用途，未有參與場上即時的判決，到今季正式在英超全數380場賽事中運作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.fanpiece.com/cornerflagnews/英超裁判檢討VAR運作-主席承認VAR四次睇漏眼-c1357060.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fcornerflagnews%2F%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E6%AA%A2%E8%A8%8EVAR%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C-%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8DVAR%E5%9B%9B%E6%AC%A1%E7%9D%87%E6%BC%8F%E7%9C%BC-c1357060.html&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=a37734ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://football.fanpiece.com/cornerflagnews/英超裁判檢討VAR運作-主席承認VAR四次睇漏眼-c1357060.html</a>"}]}